<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Forge1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Forge,</orth> subst. a furnace in which iron is heated and beaten into form: <bibl n="shak. tro 4.5.255" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 5, 255</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 4.2.74" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 2, 74</bibl>. Tropically: <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.2.239" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 2, 239</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 5.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V Chor.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h5 5.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V Chor.</bibl>
